---
title: Mediterranean Style Chicken, Chorizo and Avocado Sunshine Salad with Greek Style Cheese, Pesto Drizzle and Roasted Veg
description: A bowl of summer sun, this Mediterranean Style Chicken Breast, Chorizo and Avocado Sunshine Salad is perfect for a balanced lifestyle. Inspired by Greek and Italian cuisines whilst heroing fresh veg, this is sure to hit the spot.
